se_1.jpg","navigation_label":"Phase 1","subheading":"","title":"Inception","content":"<p> Doeraa was founded by a group of fashion-conscious individuals who wanted to create a brand that would empower consumers to make a positive impact on the world through their fashion choices.<\/p>"}},"template--16605951230206__cc0a9809-30ca-40a6-8fbc-12ca9f1f73b0-166971459697f2b806-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_2_11e1bb2d-147f-4801-937f-1f5df4c099df.jpg","navigation_label":"Phase 2","subheading":"","title":"Early days","content":"<p>In the early days, Doeraa focused on sourcing sustainable materials and working with skilled artisans to create a range of stylish and functional fashion products that were made with the consumer in mind.<\/p>"}},"template--16605951230206__cc0a9809-30ca-40a6-8fbc-12ca9f1f73b0-166971459697f2b806-2":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_3.jpg","navigation_label":"Phase 3","subheading":"","title":"Growth and expansion","content":"<p>As Doeraa gained popularity among fashion-conscious consumers, the brand expanded its offerings to include a wider range of products and began collaborating with more artisans from around the world.<\/p>"}},"4bcb8ec6-2851-421e-a496-d43ad23f4006":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_4.jpg","navigation_label":"Phase 4","subheading":"","title":"Commitment to sustainability","content":"<p>Doeraa became known for its commitment to sustainability, and the brand implemented various initiatives to reduce its environmental impact and support ethical and sustainable practices in the production of its fashion products.<br\/><\/p>"}},"192e8e2d-e5ec-43d2-bb86-09a702fbf8b6":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Phase_5.jpg","navigation_label":"Phase 5","subheading":"","title":"Giving back","content":"<p>In addition to its focus on sustainability, Doeraa also made a commitment to giving back to the community, and began donating a portion of its profits to charitable causes around the world. Today, Doeraa is a well-respected fashion brand that is known for its commitment to sustainability, social responsibility, and creating products that are not only stylish, but also have a positive impact on the world.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--16605951230206__cc0a9809-30ca-40a6-8fbc-12ca9f1f73b0-166971459697f2b806-0","template--16605951230206__cc0a9809-30ca-40a6-8fbc-12ca9f1f73b0-166971459697f2b806-1","template--16605951230206__cc0a9809-30ca-40a6-8fbc-12ca9f1f73b0-166971459697f2b806-2","4bcb8ec6-2851-421e-a496-d43ad23f4006","192e8e2d-e5ec-43d2-bb86-09a702fbf8b6"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":true,"show_impact_text_in_slide":true,"impact_text_ratio":1,"background":"","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","impact_text_color":"","impact_text_gradient":""}},"d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-0":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Kumud_sharma.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Kumud Sharma","title":"","content":"<p> First i was unsure about ordering any stuff. I thought to give it a try. But i am happy with their service. I ordered a blouse piece which was as given in image. The material is also worth every penny.Delivery was also prompt.Would definitely like to purchase more.Thank You so much<\/p>"}},"4ccaf20f-a68a-4987-83b6-bc29886feef9":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Suchanda_biswas_chakrobarti.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Suchanda Biswas Chakraborty","title":"","content":"<p>I fell in love with the material that i bought. The exact material was delivered which i saw and ordered. The delivery was very smooth and fast. I am gonna purchase more and recommend everyone else. The collection is also awesome.<\/p>"}},"7620c76a-4745-487e-8d11-c6e595ef7b9c":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Snigdha_k.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":4,"author":"Snigdha K1","title":"","content":"<p>I am impressed with the fabric and with how fast they delivered it!! Can't wait to order more!!:)<\/p>"}},"c5cd8187-952e-43aa-b03b-267f92fde3b4":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Rahul_chandra.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Rahul Chandra","title":"","content":"<p>Received the order in record time.Very happy with delivery.Not to mention the quality of product is very good<\/p>"}},"05381fca-24bb-4770-a1fd-713e424944ad":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Nandita_dad.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Nandita Da","title":"","content":"<p>Beautiful fabric. The colours are so beautiful and vibrant.Excellent quality.<\/p>"}},"template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-2":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ankita_Maddi.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":4,"author":"Ankita Maddi","title":"","content":"<p>My first order with them was during pandemic when I had no option to purchase from anywhere for my sister's wedding. I was clueless, I trusted my gut be their website seemed quite trust worthy. I went ahead, placed my first order and the heaps of praises I got for that dress was unbelievable. Now when the pandemic is over and we again have plenty options I placed an order with them again for my brother's wedding. Their quality is just ❤️ Just as shown in the pictures. I love it when brands are transparent and do justice to their claims. You have my heart DOERAA🤍<\/p>"}},"template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-1":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Ashmita_lahiri.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Ashmita Lahiri","title":"","content":"<p>Absolutely wonderful material. I've been buying from Doeraa for quite some time. The products are exactly like the description, sometimes even better than the descriptions! Ever since I've started buying from them, I've not bought any fabric from any other websites!There's a whatsapp number. The executives return to queries, sort any issue sooner than expected!Doeraa is a must choice for whoever in love with quality and stylish fabrics. They have a huge range of products from casual to formal. Thank you Doeraa!<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-0","4ccaf20f-a68a-4987-83b6-bc29886feef9","7620c76a-4745-487e-8d11-c6e595ef7b9c","c5cd8187-952e-43aa-b03b-267f92fde3b4","05381fca-24bb-4770-a1fd-713e424944ad","template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-2","template--16605951230206__d90ecc8e-c8b0-401d-af89-6a57543c94eb-1669705058a6a57717-1"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"stack_testimonials":false,"subheading":"","title":"Customer Testimonials","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"","background":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","heading_color":"","heading_gradient":"","testimonial_card_background":"#ffffff","testimonial_card_text_color":""}},"d7f7c05a-2306-4fb9-98a7-27e0c3a7d559":{"type":"blog-posts","blocks":{"template--16605951230206__d7f7c05a-2306-4fb9-98a7-27e0c3a7d559-16697042295ea60922-0":{"type":"blog","settings":{"blog":"doeraa-diaries","posts_count":3,"stack_items":false}}},"block_order":["template--16605951230206__d7f7c05a-2306-4fb9-98a7-27e0c3a7d559-16697042295ea60922-0"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"show_excerpt":true,"show_date":true,"show_author":false,"show_comments_count":false,"show_category":true,"subheading":"","title":"Blog Posts","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"","background":"#ffffff","background_gradient":"","text_color":"